author: quoctruong
message:
Change RBE Docker image to support CUDA 13.0

This is not changing the RBE machine image itself but the docker image launched on the machine.

PiperOrigin-RevId: 802736624

     # The `ml-build-rbe`'s base image is `nvidia/cuda:12.3.2-base-ubuntu22.04` which has nvidia driver installed.
